                        <p id="TheAdditionOfThisSymbolToADangerOrW-3769DD74" class="- topic/p "> The addition of
this symbol to a “Danger” or “Warning”
safety message indicates that an electrical hazard exists which will
result in personal injury if the instructions are not followed.</p>
