                        <p id="ThisIsTheSafetyAlertSymbol.ItIsUsed-3769DF3A" class="- topic/p "> This is the safety
alert symbol. It is used to alert you to potential personal injury
hazards. Obey all safety messages with this symbol to avoid possible
injury or death.</p>
